Job Interview Test Case.

Only controllers.Siroop and models.Product, models.Feature and the views/productsResult.scala.html
are relevant.

Relies on a local elastic-search server running with the data in es-data - Hint: use docker:
`docker run -d --name siroop-es -v yourpath-to/es-config/elasticsearch.yml:/usr/share/elasticsearch/config/elasticsearch.yml -v yourpath-to/es-data:/usr/share/elasticsearch/data -p 9200:9200 -p 9300:9300 elasticsearch:2.3.3
